OL,3,CWater bosses 'will face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges' over sewage dumping
OL,6,FWater bosses will face criminal
OL,7,Fcharges and be stripped of their
OL,8,Fbonuses over illegal sewage dumping,
OL,9,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FNew laws he is introducing to
OL,13,FParliament will "give regulators more
OL,14,Fteeth", he wrote in the Mail on Sunday.
