OL,3,CWater bosses 'will face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges' over sewage dumping
OL,6,F"Water bosses responsible for repeated
OL,7,Fillegal sewage dumping will face
OL,8,Fcriminal charges, and I'll ban the
OL,9,Fpayment of their multimillion-pound
OL,10,Fbonuses until they clean up their
OL,11,Ftoxic filth," the cabinet minister
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FHe said it is currently "more
OL,15,Fprofitable to let the pollution flow
OL,16,Frather than fix the broken pipes" and
OL,17,Fthat regulation is too weak to stop it.
