OL,3,CWater bosses 'will face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges' over sewage dumping
OL,6,F"This should never have been allowed
OL,7,Fto happen, and, with our new Labour
OL,8,Fgovernment, it will never happen
OL,9,Fagain."
OL,11,FMr Reed could not say what level of
OL,12,Fdumping would need to happen before
OL,13,Fcriminal charges would be triggered.
OL,15,FHe said: "What I want to do is clean
OL,16,Fup our water. We'll do it by making
OL,17,Fthe water bosses face criminal charges
OL,18,Fif they are responsible for
OL,19,Fpersistent, severe levels of illegal
OL,20,Fsewage dumping.
