OL,3,CWater bosses 'will face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges' over sewage dumping
OL,6,F"We will ban the payment of their
OL,7,Fmultimillion-pound bonuses while
OL,8,Fthey're overseeing that kind of
OL,9,Ffailure.
OL,11,F"We will ring-fence customers' money
OL,12,Fthat is earmarked for spending on
OL,13,Finvesting in the sewer system. So, if
OL,14,Fit's not spent on that, it will be
OL,15,Frefunded to customers in a discount on
OL,16,Ftheir bills."
OL,18,FHe also said he will not temporarily
OL,19,Fnationalise Thames Water because it
OL,20,Fremains financially viable.
