OL,6,FHe said there is "no need to have
OL,7,Fundue concerns at the moment" and that
OL,8,Fthere is "no threat to water supply".
OL,10,FThames Water has had its credit rating
OL,11,Fdowngraded to "junk" status by
OL,12,Finfluential ratings agency Moody's,
OL,13,Findicating that the credit agency firm
OL,14,Fthinks the utilities company is likely
OL,15,Fto default on its debt and may add to
OL,16,Fits financial pressures.
OL,18,FRegulator Ofwat has said it will
OL,19,Fimpose a "turnaround oversight regime"
OL,20,Fon Thames Water.
